    "No or faint odour, and 2.",
    "Unpleasant/offensive/putrid.",
    "The peri-ulcer condition involves the subgroups: none, erythema/redness, oedema/swelling, hyperkeratosis, pale, or macerated.",
    "And last, dressing used on the wound has the options of none, gauze, promogran, urgo, inadine, idosorb, collagenase, and others.",
